Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:18.57,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}GO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:30.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Where is the truths
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:33.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}今無情一帯の世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Here is no truths
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}栄光もなく奪い合う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:39.97,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}It's like a party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:42.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}交錯する者たちよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:44.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}突き進め果てるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:46.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}勝者と敗者どちらも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:47.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}maybe something crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:49.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}What can I belive?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:52.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}そんな問いなんで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:54.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}No one answer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:03:00.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}すべてこの虚空の中消えてった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:05.20,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}今はBREAK OUT BREAK OUT進めよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.62,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:11.83,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}その意志を揚げて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:14.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}さあもっとBREAK OUT BREAK OUT世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.09,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:21.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}切り開け迷っても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:24.05,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}So we gatta just go crazy,crazy and mad
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:25.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}just go crazy now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:28.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}dance,dance crazy ,crazy and mad
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:31.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}夢か地獄かGO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:18.57,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}GO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:30.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真理何处寻觅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:33.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}眼前这冷酷无情的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.13,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真理无从寻觅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}仅有肮脏的抢与夺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:39.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}就像一场派对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:42.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}命运纵横交错的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:44.72,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向着终点一意前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:46.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}无论胜者或败者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:47.52,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}或许某物已然疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:49.73,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}何物可信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:52.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}如此疑问为何…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:54.44,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}无人作答
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:03:00.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}一切尽皆消失在这片虚无之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:05.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}现在BREAK OUT BREAK OUT  前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.62,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:11.83,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}高举这份决心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:14.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}来吧  继续BREAK OUT BREAK OUT突破
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:21.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}世界的束缚  即使迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:24.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我们只需变得疯狂  疯而狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:25.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}如今只需变得疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:28.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}舞蹈  舞至疯狂  疯而狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:31.52,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}梦或地狱  GO CRY GO
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:17.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}破滅さえ　厭わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.90,0:22:35.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}ねえ、まだこの手に残る欠片だって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:44.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}貴方のもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:51.47,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}何もかも　失くしても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:55.68,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}捧げるものが　在るの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.31,0:23:03.19,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}未来だって　命でさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:14.16,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}焼け尽きた感情も　不毛な祈りも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.29,0:23:20.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}縋る無様も　貢ぐ愚かも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.21,0:23:26.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}病んだ声も　穢れた両手も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.71,0:23:35.27,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}傷で裂かれた心も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:17.48,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}连毁灭  都不曾厌弃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.90,0:22:35.08,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}听我说  这依旧留在手中的残片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:44.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}也是属于你之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:51.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}即便失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:55.68,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}依旧要拿出奉献之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.31,0:23:03.19,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}无论是未来  亦或生命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:14.16,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}还有燃尽的感情  和无谓的祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.29,0:23:20.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}和狼狈的纠缠  和愚昧的供奉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.21,0:23:26.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}和病态的声音  和污秽的双手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.71,0:23:35.27,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}与这受伤撕裂的心
